  "title": "Midbrain",
  "body_html": "<div>The RCEM expects candidates to be aware of the following:<br /><br /><ul><li>The midbrain lies predominantly within the posterior cranial fossa. The aperture in the tentorium cerebelli lies on its dorsal surface.</li></ul><br /><ul><li>Blood supply: primarily from posterior cerebral and superior cerebellar arteries (ex- basilar). See below</li></ul><br /><div class=\"text-center\"><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb417b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb417.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/circle of willis'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb417b.png'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></div></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodylinks\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodymedia\"></div>\n\n\n<div id=\"categorynum\">1</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategorynum\">2</div>\n\n<div id=\"categoryname\">Anatomy</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategoryname\">Head & neck</div>\n<div id=\"mybody\">\n\n<div id=\"body_content\">\nThe RCEM expects candidates to be aware of the following:<br /><br /><ul><li>The midbrain lies predominantly within the posterior cranial fossa. The aperture in the tentorium cerebelli lies on its dorsal surface.</li></ul><br /><ul><li>Blood supply: primarily from posterior cerebral and superior cerebellar arteries (ex- basilar). See below</li></ul><br /><div class=\"text-center\"><table><tr><td align = 'left' colspan='2'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb417b.png'><img class='ajaximage' src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb417.png'/></a></td></tr><tr><td valign='top' align='left'> <span style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;'>Image sourced from </span><a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/circle of willis'  target='_blank' style = 'font-size:11px; color:LightGray;' >Wikipedia</a></td><td align='right'><a data-fancybox class='fancybox lbmagglasslink' rel='group' href='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/images_MRCEMnotes/swb417b.png'><img src='https://d20g8jnrcgqmxh.cloudfront.net/css/images/mag_glass.png'/></a></td></tr></table></div></div>\n\n\n<BR><BR><br><br></div>",
